narration_text: #C C adjusts the camera
#C C picks up a lid
#C C carries the lid towards the electric stove
#C C covers the pan with the lid
#C C walks towards the sink
#C C turns on the kitchen faucet
#C C twists the kitchen faucet
#C C picks the spoon and the chopsticks
#C C puts the spoon and the chopsticks in the sink
#C C picks up the sponge
#C C picks up the kitchen detergent
#C C sprinkles the kitchen detergent on the sponge
#C C puts the kitchen detergent back
#C C picks up the bowl
#C C pours the water from the bowl into the sink
#C C washes the bowl using the sponge
#C C puts the bowl on the sink
#C C picks up the chopsticks
#C C washes the chopsticks
#C C puts the chopsticks on the bowl
#C C picks up the spoon
#C C washes the spoon using the sponge
#C C puts back the sponge
#C C rinses the spoon
#C C puts the spoon on the utensils rack
#C C rinses the chopsticks
#C C puts the chopsticks on the utensils rack
#C C rinses the bowl
#C C puts the bowl on the countertop
#C C picks up the sponge
#C C cleans the sink using the sponge
#C C throws the sponge into the sponge rack
#C C picks up the kitchen towel
#C C turns off the kitchen faucet
#C C dries the sink using the kitchen towel
#C C turns the kitchen towel
#C C dries the sink using the kitchen towel
#C C puts the kitchen towel on the countertop
#C C picks up the kitchen detergent
#C C sprays the kitchen sink with the kitchen detergent
#C C puts back the kitchen detergent
#C C twists the kitchen faucet
#C C turns on the kitchen faucet
#C C turns off the kitchen faucet
#C C rinses off the hand
#C C wipes the hand off
#C C adjusts the camera
